   <p xml:id="60" begin="00:01:46.725" end="00:01:48.660">THROUGH IT THERE IS NO<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="61" begin="00:01:47.793" end="00:01:50.496">ACCEPTANCE OF THE FACT THAT<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="62" begin="00:01:48.794" end="00:01:52.097">THEY MIGHT HAVE -- AT SOME<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="63" begin="00:01:50.629" end="00:01:52.498">POINT, BROUGHT THIS ON<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="64" begin="00:01:52.231" end="00:01:55.367">THEMSELVES.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="65" begin="00:01:52.631" end="00:01:56.735">&gt;&gt; EVERY POINT DUGARD, AT<br/></p>
