   <p xml:id="68" begin="00:01:57.803" end="00:02:00.539">THEY ATTACKED EVERYBODY.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="69" begin="00:01:58.837" end="00:02:02.674">YOU GO TO HEIR REGIME THAT<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="70" begin="00:02:00.672" end="00:02:04.276">TODAY AND AS YOU MENTIONED<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="71" begin="00:02:02.808" end="00:02:05.944">THE WAR MUSEUM IN TOKYO,<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="72" begin="00:02:04.409" end="00:02:10.315">WHAT YOU GET THERE IS WE<br/></p>
