   <p xml:id="79" begin="00:02:19.191" end="00:02:21.093">A-BOMB?<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="80" begin="00:02:19.525" end="00:02:22.094">&gt;&gt; VERY, VERY SUBTLE.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="81" begin="00:02:21.227" end="00:02:23.796">SHOWS A LOT OF THINGS LIKE<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="82" begin="00:02:22.228" end="00:02:28.434">THE MUSHROOM CLOUD AND THERE<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="83" begin="00:02:23.929" end="00:02:29.501">IS A LOT OF VICTIMIZATION<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="84" begin="00:02:28.567" end="00:02:30.636">AND YES IT WAS A HORRIBLE<br/></p>
