   <p xml:id="91" begin="00:02:37.276" end="00:02:39.511">FIGHTING UNTIL IT FINALLY<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="92" begin="00:02:38.277" end="00:02:40.246">CAME TO THE POINT THEY COULD<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="93" begin="00:02:39.645" end="00:02:42.081">NOT FIGHT ANYMORE.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="94" begin="00:02:40.379" end="00:02:43.215">&gt;&gt; WE MAKE THAT QUITE CLEAR<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="95" begin="00:02:42.214" end="00:02:47.219">THAT THE JAPANESE WERE NOT<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="96" begin="00:02:43.349" end="00:02:48.554">READY TO SURRENDER AT ALL<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="97" begin="00:02:47.353" end="00:02:49.488">DUGARD AND I HAD A VERY HARD<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="98" begin="00:02:48.687" end="00:02:50.356">TIME GETTING CLEARANCE FOR<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="99" begin="00:02:49.622" end="00:02:52.791">CERTAIN DOCUMENTS AND<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="100" begin="00:02:50.489" end="00:02:53.526">PICTURES WE WANTED TO USE<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="101" begin="00:02:52.925" end="00:02:55.294">FROM THE JAPANESE.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="102" begin="00:02:53.659" end="00:02:56.462">AND FINALLY THEY SAID NO.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="103" begin="00:02:55.427" end="00:02:56.729">THEY WOULDN'T GIVE IT TO US.<br/></p>
