   <p xml:id="105" begin="00:02:56.862" end="00:03:00.332">&gt;&gt; THE PROBLEM IS THE<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="106" begin="00:02:58.998" end="00:03:02.168">HIROSHIMA PEACEFUL MUSEUM<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="107" begin="00:03:00.466" end="00:03:04.370">WHERE OBAMA IS GOING TO BE<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="108" begin="00:03:02.301" end="00:03:06.739">SPEAKING, OWNS THE RIGHTS TO<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="109" begin="00:03:04.503" end="00:03:08.140">THE AN DICK DOTES AND<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="110" begin="00:03:06.873" end="00:03:08.541">VIGNETTES FROM ALL THESE<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="111" begin="00:03:08.274" end="00:03:09.675">SURVIVORS.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="112" begin="00:03:08.674" end="00:03:10.643">AND THEIR JOB WAS TO GET<br/></p>
