   <p xml:id="117" begin="00:03:15.181" end="00:03:16.883">HORROR OF WHAT HAPPENED.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="118" begin="00:03:15.848" end="00:03:17.884">&gt;&gt; DID YOU EXPLAIN THE<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="119" begin="00:03:17.016" end="00:03:18.851">KILLING BOOKS REACHED<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="120" begin="00:03:18.017" end="00:03:20.720">MILLIONS AND MILLIONS AND<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="121" begin="00:03:18.985" end="00:03:21.521">THE BEST SELLING NONFICTION<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="122" begin="00:03:20.853" end="00:03:23.256">BOOKS IN THE WORLD?<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="123" begin="00:03:21.654" end="00:03:23.990">DID YOU EXPLAIN THAT?<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="124" begin="00:03:23.389" end="00:03:25.691">&gt;&gt; IT DIDN'T MATTER.<br/></p>
