   <p xml:id="142" begin="00:03:49.916" end="00:03:52.418">THEY DON'T LIKE THE BOOK<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="143" begin="00:03:52.218" end="00:03:54.287">ANYWAY.<br/></p>
   <p xml:id="144" begin="00:03:52.552" end="00:03:55.388">&gt;&gt; I THINK IT'S ONE OF THE<br/></p>
